txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Bent metal maces from hostile warriors in western Dunland. Collect them and deliver them to the taskmaster in Galtrev to earn favour with the Men of Dunland.
'The common folk of Dunland are often beset by those who would prey upon our weakness. You have taught them a lesson, and we thank you for it.'
'There are villains of every stripe lurking in Dunland these days -- would that we had only the Rohirrim to fear....'
Men of Dunland Task: Bent Metal Maces
The Dunlending taskmaster wants bent metal maces. She can be found at Galtrev in Pren Gwydh.
Deliver the bent metal maces to the taskmaster in Galtrev.
You have accepted a task to acquire bent metal maces. You are to deliver them to the Dunlending taskmaster in Galtrev.
Wanted: Bent metal maces from hostile warriors in western Dunland.
